title: bubblegum bitches & barbie dolls
body:
read it on the AO3 at https://ift.tt/2FwZWnA

by daegutaegi

yoongi was sent to kill someone but he ended up in the wrong apartment, finding tiny college boy taehyung watching tv while eating dinner.

he’s in the middle of apologizing for breaking through the kid’s window when he felt a cold metal pressing against the back of his neck.

“did he hurt you, taehyungie?” another boy asks from behind him, standing so close to yoongi and smelling like bubblegum all over.

“no its okay, even if he did i could’ve handled it by myself” taehyung huffed, kicking his baby blue gun with his feet back under the couch.

and thats how yoongi ended up in kitty gang’s apartment.

body:
Rant:7/Forever

I was pondering about my life these past couple of hours and I have come to the conclusion that I have 1 friend. Now I feel like even that one person is sick of me. It’s so sad and I can’t help wondering what is it about me that people can’t get along with? It’s frustrating at these points in my life when I need comfort but cannot lean on anybody to trust because I think I have lost the basic ability to trust a person with me. Is it just me or does anyone else feel like that?
